output_repo_commit_message: Small test run of CADET-Core verification simulations;

Reduced run to verify CADET-Core v5.0.3 release;
Convergence test for the FV-discretized linear 2DGRM with 3 zones to be used in Rao et al. (2025);
Convergence test for the linear systems in Frandsen et al. (2025b);
